      "originalText": "❌  Compute-bound to one host — won't scale\n❌  Lower model quality (7B–13B vs Haiku)\n❌  Can't serve multiple clients at once\n❌  High token cost at the extraction step\n❌  No summarization ≠ more context\n      Just more tokens to the capable model",
